  "summary_md": "### CRM Call: Supply Chain Dashboard – Progress and Issues\n\nThe project team convened for a scheduled update call regarding Northwind Traders' supply chain dashboard implementation. Aaliyah Brooks (Adatum) opened with a recap of recent deployment activities, followed by Lisa Taylor (Northwind) raising concerns over missing data feed logs from last week's automated batch run. Terrence Wu reported intermittent errors in dashboard widgets displaying inventory metrics. Marcus Patel (Adatum) acknowledged the technical issues and committed to investigate log discrepancies. The team agreed that improved file transfer reliability is crucial to achieving milestone delivery by next week. Client requests included a status update on corrected data feeds and technical clarification on inventory mapping logic. Adatum confirmed intention to resend logs securely and address widget behavior. Actions and commitments were set to ensure timeline alignment and client satisfaction.\n\n#### Key Decisions & Discussion Points\n- Acknowledge and troubleshoot missing/corrupted data logs\n- Clarify dashboard inventory mapping logic for client operations\n- Enhance reliability of future data file transfers\n- Maintain weekly cadence for project update calls",
  "action_items": [
    {
      "owner": {
        "name": "Marcus Patel",
        "email": "marcus.patel@adatum.com"
      },
      "description": "Review last week's automated batch log transfer for missing or corrupted entries. Coordinate with engineering to identify root causes, prepare a corrected log file, and resend to Northwind via secure link by Wednesday. Confirm delivery with client after successful transfer.",
      "due_date": "2024-06-05"
    },
    {
      "owner": {
        "name": "Aaliyah Brooks",
        "email": "aaliyah.brooks@adatum.com"
      },
      "description": "Draft and send a technical explanation to Lisa Taylor covering inventory mapping logic as used in the dashboard, to clarify how source data maps to operational categories. Ensure documentation is sent as part of the weekly client update before Friday.",
      "due_date": "2024-06-07"
    },
    {
      "owner": {
        "name": "Terrence Wu",
        "email": "terrence.wu@northwindtraders.com"
      },
      "description": "Collect details and screenshots regarding intermittent widget errors observed in the dashboard. Share findings with Adatum team for root cause analysis prior to the next status call.",
      "due_date": "2024-06-06"
    }
  ],
  "issue_flags": [
    "Missing/corrupted data feed logs",
    "Intermittent dashboard widget errors",
    "Need for timeline clarification on handoffs"
  ],
  "external_commitments": [
    {
      "commitment": "Adatum will investigate data feed log transfer issues and provide Northwind with a corrected set of logs by Wednesday, ensuring secure delivery and follow-up confirmation.",
      "date": "2024-06-03",
      "owner": {
        "name": "Marcus Patel",
        "email": "marcus.patel@adatum.com"
      }
    },
    {
      "commitment": "Adatum will share detailed documentation on inventory mapping logic to address recent client queries, sent no later than close of business Friday.",
      "date": "2024-06-03",
      "owner": {
        "name": "Aaliyah Brooks",
        "email": "aaliyah.brooks@adatum.com"
      }
    }
  ],
  "internal_comments": [
    {
      "author": "Aaliyah Brooks",
      "email": "aaliyah.brooks@adatum.com",
      "comment": "Client is closely watching delivery timing this week and raised concern over recurring log issues. Ensure extra diligence on file integrity before resending."
    },
    {
      "author": "Marcus Patel",
      "email": "marcus.patel@adatum.com",
      "comment": "Widget errors seem related to recent source data changes; engineering needs to review new mappings. Good opportunity to clarify logic for client and prevent future confusion."
    }
  ]
}

