          "name": "Casey Morgan",
          "email": "casey.morgan@adatum.com",
          "role": "Client Success Specialist, Adatum Corporation"
        }
      ],
      "summary_md": "**Discussion focused on initial end-to-end data connection validation for the new supply chain dashboard.** Violet Martinez raised specifics around ensuring on-time ingestion of daily order and inventory feeds, especially for the NA/EU regions. Marcus Patel presented the status of automated import scripts – integration with Northwind's SFTP server was 80% complete, with a successful dry run on prior week's data. Several error-handling edge cases (such as partial day file arrivals) were flagged, and Violet noted the importance of downstream alerting for data freshness. Casey confirmed the next checkpoint will prioritize exception logging visibility so that Northwind can audit delays in real-time. All parties agreed that an additional QA cycle on Monday, June 17th should determine readiness for internal UAT. **Actions and concerns centered on timely data flows and operational transparency.**",
      "flagged_issues": [
        "Delayed delivery of daily inventory feed (NA region)",
        "Limited visibility into error alerting on partial uploads"
      ],
      "next_steps": [
        "Marcus Patel to finalize automated import scripts and report error handling status by 2024-06-14",
        "Casey Morgan to share proposed data exception logging views with Northwind team by 2024-06-13"
      ],
      "commitments_made": [
        {
          "topic": "Automated Data Imports Ready for UAT",
          "promised_by": "marcus.patel@adatum.com",
          "commitment_date": "2024-06-14T12:00:00-04:00",
          "description": "Marcus Patel will ensure that the end-to-end automated import scripts, including robust error handling and alert generation, are ready for Northwind’s UAT process by the June 14 checkpoint. This includes written confirmation and a sample error log for validation purposes.",
          "client_visible": true
        },
        {
          "topic": "Internal error handling workflow review",
          "promised_by": "casey.morgan@adatum.com",
