          "description": "Casey Morgan to conduct an Adatum-only technical review of the error-handling workflow to identify any security or compliance gaps prior to client handoff. This is for internal process readiness and will not be shared outside Adatum.",
          "client_visible": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "date": "2024-06-14T11:30:00-04:00",
      "participants": [
        {
          "name": "Violet Martinez",
          "email": "violet.martinez@northwindtraders.com",
          "role": "Lead Contact, Supply Chain Transformation"
        },
        {
          "name": "Mario Rogers",
          "email": "mario.rogers@adatum.com",
          "role": "Product Manager, Adatum Corporation"
        },
        {
          "name": "Casey Morgan",
          "email": "casey.morgan@adatum.com",
          "role": "Client Success Specialist, Adatum Corporation"
        }
      ],
      "summary_md": "**The call provided an overview of planned dashboard features and staged rollout.** Early user feedback and change requests from Northwind were discussed, particularly regarding metrics granularity at the warehouse level and support for custom alert thresholds. Mario Rogers summarized the product team’s current timeline: staging release tentatively on June 21, pending final QA, with targeted enablement materials for Northwind’s warehouse leads shared in advance. Violet Martinez emphasized the need for a walkthrough prior to live deployment given cross-functional impact. Mario confirmed that at least one joint walkthrough session will be scheduled for June 19 and all feedback incorporated before go-live. **Risks around stretching timeline due to user acceptance and training documentation finalization were acknowledged.**",
      "flagged_issues": [
        {
          "issue": "Timeline risk due to new requirements on metrics customization"
        }
      ],
      "next_steps": [
        "Mario Rogers to organize dashboard walkthrough for Northwind stakeholders by 2024-06-19",
        "Casey Morgan to circulate enablement documentation to Violet Martinez by 2024-06-18"
      ],
      "commitments_made": [
        {
          "topic": "Dashboard Walkthrough Scheduling",
          "promised_by": "mario.rogers@adatum.com",
          "commitment_date": "2024-06-17T16:00:00-04:00",
          "description": "Mario Rogers committed to confirm and invite Northwind project stakeholders to a comprehensive dashboard walkthrough and Q&A session. This session will cover new metric features, data visualization options, and custom alert logic, targeting completion by mid-week.",
          "client_visible": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "date": "2024-06-18T09:30:00-04:00",
      "participants": [
        {
          "name": "Violet Martinez",
          "email": "violet.martinez@northwindtraders.com",
          "role": "Lead Contact, Supply Chain Transformation"
        },
        {
          "name": "Marcus Patel",
          "email": "marcus.patel@adatum.com",
          "role": "Data Integration Lead, Adatum Corporation"
        }
      ],
      "summary_md": "**Final QA and pre-UAT status review for dashboard integration.** Violet Martinez joined to validate that all Northwind data feeds (orders, inventory, and shipment) were being captured with expected update frequencies and latency under typical loads. Marcus Patel demonstrated new inline error reporting; Violet confirmed that dashboard data latency now matches Northwind’s SLA (30 min max). They also reviewed recent backlog items from Northwind’s support desk and agreed that the next improvement cycle would tackle two remaining low-priority exceptions. Marcus explained that two documentation items (API change log and exception audit trails) are in internal review ahead of client release. **Overall, discussion reaffirmed on-track status for pilot rollout, with mutual agreement on outstanding items and sequencing.**",
      "flagged_issues": [],
      "next_steps": [
        "Marcus Patel to release API change log and exception audit documentation to Northwind by 2024-06-20"
      ],
      "commitments_made": [
        {
          "topic": "Release of documentation to client",
          "promised_by": "marcus.patel@adatum.com",
          "commitment_date": "2024-06-20T10:00:00-04:00",
