      "status": "completed",
      "description": "Internal-only review of error handling processes for dashboard integration, evaluating security, compliance, and capacity for scaling incident alerting workflows before next client-facing demo. Results documented in Adatum's internal risk log.",
      "client_visible": false
    },
    {
      "date": "2024-06-23T15:00:00-04:00",
      "topic": "Alert builder logic fix deployment schedule",
      "promised_by": "mario.rogers@adatum.com",
      "status": "pending",
      "description": "Performance improvements for alert builder feature, including regression-tested code and new documentation of latency benchmarks, to be released to Northwind’s production environment by deadline. Communication of updated metrics to follow within same business day.",
